<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.5.4">
<l>paḷḷattil mēyum paṟavai yurukkoṇṭu</l>
<l>kaḷḷava curaṉ varuvāṉait tāṉkaṇṭu</l>
<l>puḷḷitu veṉṟu potukkōvāy kīṇṭiṭṭa</l>
<l>piḷḷaiyai vantukuḻal vārāyak kākkāy</l>
<l rend="indent">pēymulaiyuṇ ṭāṉkuḻal vārāyak kākkāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come to the child</l>
<l rend="indent"> who, having seen he who came as a deceptive demon</l>
<l rend="indent">with the form of a bird hunting in a waterhole,</l>
<l rend="indent">thinking ‘it is a bird’, quickly split [its] mouth</l>
<l>Caw! Caw!Comb [his] curly hair.</l>
<l>Caw! Caw! Comb the curly hair of he who drank for the breast of the demon.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
